snippet.title: Filmweb
snippet.description:
FILMWEBTV is a part of Filmweb.no.

What does our channel offer? In addition to the newest movie trailers you will find interviews done by our reporter with the biggest movie stars of Hollywood. 

Join in on our conversations with actors and directors on their latest films. Tell us what you think in the comment section. 

Get your cinema tickets for Norway at www.filmweb.no

Copyright FilmwebTV 2015.
